Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓬萊的玉枝紮根成了巨樹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其靈力彌漫於整個空間中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霧變濃時要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內心的願望會變成幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們真的到畫裡面來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是水墨畫的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵醬 妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生物都是有顏色的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是蓬萊玉枝長成的靈樹的影響吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是孕育生命的靈樹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以創造出了多彩的生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們又要鬧彆扭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有鬧彆扭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幼稚鬼銀次總是這麼固執
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:02:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓我費心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:02:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一如既往的粗暴態度才令人吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們快去找蓬萊的玉枝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別指手畫腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,津場木葵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵醬 我們去哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去山上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先順著七彩的靈力到山頂上看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個靈力應該會告訴你們蓬萊的玉枝的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要爬山了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別慢呑呑的兩個下人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是…什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是縫陰大人的小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,縫陰大人和律子夫人都說過他們很喜歡讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先在這裡躲一躲雨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帶了熱飲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有熱可可哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼「真好啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們必須在明天傍晚之前把蓬萊的玉枝帶回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這麼大的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算下雨我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 蘭丸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是為了雨一停就能動身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先去前面探路了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次先生很瞭解蘭丸的舉動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得自己對蘭丸一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可是一種香甜的東西吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸 好快啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然敢說老子可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛的狗狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比阿信更像玩偶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你個小河童
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有比信長更可愛的狗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 你的靈力消耗得真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少囉嗦 銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個空間比想像中的還要特別
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也變成獸型試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靈力也會很快消耗完的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能恢復些精力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 這個湯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱可可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加了椰奶的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:04.01,NAME,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\c&H403593&\blur6}蘭丸{\c}是「犬妖」，現實中不可以餵狗狗喝可可哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳的味覺雖然消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,料理中的靈力似乎還在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊 葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡全都是無法輕易入手的書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不塊是縫陰大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這本是常世的書
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常世的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫了大太法師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是海坊主的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大太法師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是處理人類與妖魔鬥爭所產生穢物的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當它無法除盡污穢的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類把它關進了海之盡頭的狹縫中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關起來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小不點 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵醬 快看天上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七彩的靈力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們快追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 先繼續往山頂走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你說我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再走下去就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天才是決勝負的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你說我也知道 銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤牛肉三明治還有烤蘑菇串
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜點是無花果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用折尾屋帶來的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和這個世界找到的東西混搭出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果變成了適合野餐的菜色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤牛肉三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個我最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用昨天的烤牛肉 蔬萊和佐料一起做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷工減料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 確實很美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸終於也承認妳的手藝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:08:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過是因為肚子餓罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為「空腹是最好的調味料」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的黃瓜也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去周圍看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經起霧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在行動很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒辦法像你們一樣悠閒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不重蹈三百年前的覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三百年前發生什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和這次一樣需要蓬萊的玉枝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷獸大人說會想辦法拿到手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那期間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷獸大人對磯姬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說了一些侮辱她尊嚴的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:09:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有多想便頂嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結桌雷獸大人大怒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟就這樣消失不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些全都是雷獸算計好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我頂撞他時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷獸大人擺出了「這麼容易就上鉤了」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的愉悅神情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定很希望儀式失敗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去就是個很過分的妖怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是我們失去了磯姬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著 蘭丸也變了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了守護南之地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不改變
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這麼一回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我理解這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是沒有堅持與他並肩作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你後悔來到天神屋了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒有後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因為到了天神屋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才擁有了獨一無二的經驗和相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些「獨一無二」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會對這次儀式有幫助的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然想和蘭丸談談 卻總是沒有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他面前總是忍不住和他頂嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次先生想和蘭丸回到最初的兄弟關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果蘭丸願意原諒我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定可以和好如初的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次先生大概就要留在折尾屋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 無花果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次先生 來吃無花果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熟透了的果子好軟 很好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是嚐不出味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的 葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐今後再也嚐不出味道這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不可能發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不可以發生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吃了這麼多美味的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會得到幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後妳肯定也會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:13:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為饑餓的妖怪們做很多美味佳餚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與他們分旱幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 銀次先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我以前見過面嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我還小的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磯姬..大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磯姬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次先生 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是磯姬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是白夜大人說的幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓬萊靈樹的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸也一定...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磯姬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磯姬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明叫我不要亂跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己怎麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 一副被耍了的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別逞強了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸 蘭丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳這是什麼表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才要是沒吃妳做的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能真的會死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次先生一定在找我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定還在擔心我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他擔心的大概是妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他巴不得我去死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次先生非常擔心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還問我蘭丸會不會也看到了幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次先生一直都很在意你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是親人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磯姬大人 銀次先生 還有你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,現在也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮城舊址撿來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是磯姬大人給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是真正的磯姬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從她那裡聽到了很多你和銀次先生小時候的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很擔心你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磯姬大人拜託我做海味珍饌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我卻嚐不出味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起 磯姬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.55,0:17:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次他明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無論如何都要去找蓬萊的玉枝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他會去山頂的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次一定會這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七色的靈力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虹櫻貝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那時候的貝殼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閃閃發光的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓬萊靈樹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼美麗的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸 葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:18:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:18:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆都沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要的東西就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發什麼愣呢？ 銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不許笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是很可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,津場木葵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別磨磨蹭蹭的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白夜先生的聯絡符...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:19:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白夜先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳還有很多要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘 銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 都平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順利完成使命了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都是一副又累又髒的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好努力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來就可以順利舉行儀式了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀吉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:20:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煙花大會從傍晚開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我帶蘭丸和銀次去醫務室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他們吃些回復靈力的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起藥還是料理的效果更好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就去做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐也必須去休息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一副疲憊不堪的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疲憊不堪...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳也洗個澡休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不進來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還不夠格進到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.91,0:21:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們進折尾屋的時間不長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒做什麼貢獻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.09,0:21:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們倆商量了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,津場木葵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們希望「海味珍饌」由妳來完成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:00.04,title,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蓬萊玉枝生存戰
Comment: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:03.56,songtitle,,0,0,0,,「知らない気持ち 」作詞、作曲：シンリズム，編曲：シンリズム、高野勲，主唱：中島愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:20.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}ねぇ　どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.17,0:22:25.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}慣れない手で作った苦さを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:30.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}思い出して　笑ってみたり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:33.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}遠くで暮らし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.03,0:22:39.57,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}戸惑ってた　店先までも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:43.96,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}今では私の街
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:51.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}静かすぎて　眠れない夜でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.78,0:22:59.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}平気よ　見えない糸があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.26,0:23:04.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}ここがどこだって　構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:08.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}揺れる風景とその手を取り
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.67,0:23:10.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}まだ　ちょっとだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:15.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}知らないあなたの気持ちに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.32,0:23:19.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}そっと　寄り添いたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:24.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}迷ってしまわないように
Comment: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:20.12,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}喂　為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.17,0:22:25.00,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}回想起用不習慣的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:30.30,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}創造的苦澀　卻好像在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:33.71,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}在遠方的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.03,0:22:39.57,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}不知所措地　來到的店門前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:43.96,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}現在也已是我的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:51.73,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}即便是太過寧靜　而不成眠的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.78,0:22:59.15,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}也沒事唷　因為有著看不見的絲線
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.26,0:23:04.67,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}就連這裡是哪裡　都不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:08.44,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}搖曳的風景並牽起那隻手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.67,0:23:10.28,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}還　只是有點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:15.11,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}不知道對於你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.32,0:23:19.23,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}想要悄悄地　靠近過去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:24.82,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}為了不會迷惘
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.74,0:23:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐裡先生和犬先生能和好真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.45,0:23:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也撿了好多亮閃閃的珠子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.70,0:23:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵醬要做海味珍饌了嗎？
